issues.description: The UML diagram in the problem statement defines Stock.add(String) as returning void, but both the template and the solution implementations declare it as returning int. This discrepancy between the diagram and the provided code may confuse students when reading the specification versus using the provided Stock.add method.
issues.suggested_fix: Update the UML in the problem statement to specify +add(String): int so it matches the method signature in both the template and solution.
